member to talk with your advisees Invite Career Services to your departmental meeting to share information about occupational trends in your discipline Compile a list of alumni directly related to your discipline Collect information about internships related to your major Refer employers to Career Services Refer guest speakers with employment opportunities to Career Services Attend employer Information Sessions on Post Include information about Career Services in your mailings Encourage your alumni to become a VMI Alumni Mentor VMI Foundation Keydet Club Alumni Webcams Directories My VMI  RESOURCES   Title IX  Health   Safety   IT   Site Index Parents   Families   Cadets   Non discrimination Statement   Privacy   THE VMI PHILOSOPHY The VMI experience is framed by relevant education within a military environment  It s an education that develops character  fosters a lifelong appreciation of physical fitness engenders a sense of responsibility to others  and cultivates the ability to master adversity  VIRGINIA MILITARY INSTITUTE Lexington  Virginia 24450 General Information   540  464 7230  Admissions  admissions vmi edu 